Name: uterine ligament mucinous adenocarcinoma
Definition: A uterine ligament adenocarcinoma that produces mucin.
Synonym: mucinous carcinoma of the bile duct

Name: uterine ligament clear cell adenocarcinoma
Definition: A uterine ligament adenocarcinoma that derives_from epithelial cells which have clear cytoplasm.
Synonym: Clear cell carcinoma of the fallopian tube

Name: uterine ligament serous adenocarcinoma
Definition: A uterine ligament adenocarcinoma that derives_from epithelial cells originating in glandular tissue forming serous lesions.

Name: uterine ligament endometrioid adenocarcinoma
Definition: A uterine ligament adenocarcinoma that derives_from endometrial epithelial cells of glandular origin.
